Download the fp8 flux1-dev checkpoint here and place it under models/checkpoints. It includes the two required text encoders already so they do not need to be loaded separately. 

https://huggingface.co/Comfy-Org/flux1-dev/tree/main

Tips

- Flux does not need a negative prompt when using cfg 1.0
- When you make the strength of the controlnet over 0.4, the prompt has less of an effect.
